---
title: Southeast Asian Pork & Honey-Soy Veggies with Jasmine Rice & Japanese Mayo
description: Watch out because our lovely spiced pork is going to turn some heads tonight! With all the umami, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/650394b0ddf45550bcf9f3ce-193003f9.jpeg
